01:02:27.000 --> 01:02:32.000
We're aiming for something we've thought through and that has moral principles underneath it and so on

01:02:32.000 --> 01:02:37.000
Well, maybe, I mean, we're getting... I don't want to argue about semantics here, what we mean by superorganism

01:02:37.000 --> 01:02:41.000
I'd certainly agree with what you just described as important goals

01:02:41.000 --> 01:02:47.000
It's an interesting question, are the bacteria within us...

01:02:47.000 --> 01:02:52.000
