01:06:35.000 --> 01:06:42.000
But otherwise human rights is... you have definite ideas about what they should be

01:06:42.000 --> 01:06:47.000
Of course evolution doesn't care at all about our future and that level

01:06:47.000 --> 01:06:52.000
