So you're saying there is a moral evolution?

01:08:05.000 --> 01:08:07.000
Yes, I think there is some more...

01:08:07.000 --> 01:08:10.000
Certainly moral evolution, but I think it's directed

01:08:10.000 --> 01:08:14.000
