01:08:33.000 --> 01:08:39.000
So how do you think that might play out in the future as we have tendencies

01:08:39.000 --> 01:08:44.000
You brought up that are frightening tendencies, maybe for the subsumption of the individual

01:08:44.000 --> 01:08:49.000
Into the super organism, you know, anthill

01:08:49.000 --> 01:08:57.000
Do you see that we are going to need to either invent or discover or still have to be doing that?

01:08:57.000 --> 01:08:58.000
Like there's more to come?

