Well, look, I think there are a lot of...

01:09:01.000 --> 01:09:06.000
Just as people could live in a society with chattel slavery

01:09:06.000 --> 01:09:10.000
And somehow avert their gaze and avert their mind from it

01:09:10.000 --> 01:09:16.000
Even though they knew, I mean, Jefferson knew, these people knew they were doing something wrong at a deep level

01:09:16.000 --> 01:09:21.000
But we have lots of self-rationalization, a lot of blocking, psychological blocking mechanisms

01:09:21.000 --> 01:09:25.000
To keep us from recognizing how terrible certain things we are doing

01:09:25.000 --> 01:09:29.000
